name: The Orange - #0019
description: The meaning of the circle is too broad to be written down, too limited to be something infinite. But, the circle has always been the characters that make us feel real. Looking at that shape deeper will make you realize that circle as a whole. The circles were created to become various objects which produce breath surrounding us. The biased edges and surfaces, and then a non-existent start or finish are things confirming, that a circle is the true form of nature. And orange represents all of this.
